headline: Keysight and Alea First to Validate 3GPP EUTRA Mission Critical Test Case
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., February 05, 2025--Keysight Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: KEYS) and Alea S.r.l have validated the first* mission-critical 3GPP Evolved Universal Terrestrial Radio Access (EUTRA) test case for mission-critical-push-to-talk (MCPTT) at the recent Global Certification Forum (GCF) Conformance Agreement Group (CAG) meeting. The validation was conducted using the Keysight S8704A Protocol Conformance Toolset.
